title: Active.WebCam.v10.1
description:
Active WebCam v10.1 + Patch
Active WebCam capture images at up to 30 frames per second from any device, including video cameras and USB analog boards, TV, camcorders, cameras and IP network.He conveys the content captured or can upload to an FTP server. It can also be used as a security system detect any movement in the area monitored by sending sound signals to you, email and the images captured by video recordings.
